name: GotoNextViewBehaviors
shortdesc: A collection of goto next view behavior objects.

method.name: count
method.shortdesc: Displays the number of elements in the GotoNextViewBehavior.

parameter.name: withProperties
parameter.shortdesc: Initial values for properties of the new GotoNextViewBehavior &#40;Optional)

method.name: item
method.shortdesc: Returns the GotoNextViewBehavior with the specified index or name.

parameter.name: index
parameter.shortdesc: The index or name. Can accept: Long Integer or String.

method.name: itemByName
method.shortdesc: Returns the GotoNextViewBehavior with the specified name.

method.name: itemByID
method.shortdesc: Returns the GotoNextViewBehavior with the specified ID.

method.name: itemByRange
method.shortdesc: Returns the GotoNextViewBehaviors within the specified range.

parameter.name: from
parameter.shortdesc: The GotoNextViewBehavior, index, or name at the beginning of the range. Can accept: GotoNextViewBehavior, Long Integer or String.

parameter.name: to
parameter.shortdesc: The GotoNextViewBehavior, index, or name at the end of the range. Can accept: GotoNextViewBehavior, Long Integer or String.

method.name: firstItem
method.shortdesc: Returns the first GotoNextViewBehavior in the collection.

method.name: lastItem
method.shortdesc: Returns the last GotoNextViewBehavior in the collection.

method.name: middleItem
method.shortdesc: Returns the middle GotoNextViewBehavior in the collection.

method.name: previousItem
method.shortdesc: Returns the GotoNextViewBehavior with the index previous to the specified index.

parameter.name: obj
parameter.shortdesc: The index of the GotoNextViewBehavior that follows the desired GotoNextViewBehavior.

method.name: nextItem
method.shortdesc: Returns the GotoNextViewBehavior whose index follows the specified GotoNextViewBehavior in the collection.

parameter.name: obj
parameter.shortdesc: The GotoNextViewBehavior whose index comes before the desired GotoNextViewBehavior.

method.name: anyItem
method.shortdesc: Returns any GotoNextViewBehavior in the collection.

method.name: everyItem
method.shortdesc: Returns every GotoNextViewBehavior in the collection.

method.name: toSource
method.shortdesc: Generates a string which, if executed, will return the GotoNextViewBehavior.
Returns the GotoNextViewBehavior with the specified index.

property.name: length
property.shortdesc: The number of objects in the collection.
